original: Lindsten, Carl Gunnar, bitr. länsarkitekt, Kalmar, f. 25/11/09 i Gbg av rektorn, fil. dr Carl L. o. Gina Sandberg. G. 42 m. Ann-Sofi Schotte. Barn: Carl Thomas f. 43. — Stud:ex. i Södertälje 27, arkit:ex. v. KTH 39. Anst. v. flygförvaltn. 39, h. arkit. A. V. Brunskog 40-42, v. länsarkit :kont. i Linköp. 43, assist, v. dito i Karlskrona 44-46, bitr. länsarkit. i Kalmar sed. 46.
translated: Lindsten, Carl Gunnar, Deputy County Architect, Kalmar, b. 25/11/09 in Gothenburg to the principal, PhD Carl L. and Gina Sandberg. Married in 1942 to Ann-Sofi Schotte. Children: Carl Thomas b. 1943. - Passed matriculation exam in Södertälje in 1927, graduated as an architect from the Royal Institute of Technology in 1939. Employed by the Air Administration in 1939, senior architect at A. V. Brunskog from 1940-1942, deputy county architect in Linköping from 1943, assistant at the same position in Karlskrona from 1944-1946, deputy county architect in Kalmar since 1946.
